title: Juan Bautista de Anza National Historic Trail: Parks as Classrooms
body: Parks as Classrooms        Traveling Trunks Unpack the relevance of the 1775-76 Anza Expedition, the first overland colonizing expedition to Alta California. Traveling trunks contain lesson plans and items related to Spanish colonial history and the Native cultures and landscapes of the American West.
